Summary: 2 lights off set that dimmed out one after the other
divs: Sighting DetailsFor starters I am not crazy......that being said, I was outside and looked up like I always do and saw some stars and the moon. Than I noticed 2 lights moving about 200 yards away from each other way up in the sky. They were moving too slow to be a meteor cause I see them often. The light in the front started to dim out then almost simultaneously the light behind it went out as well. There were 2 different craft cause the one in the back was off set to the left of it.
